Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I journey ahead, holding on to my lantern
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:14.08,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Ani mita potima i ji’ulyc
