Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right, I have many guardians watching over me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:32.02,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Hap’a myukil sha lu be’iru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This fortune will surely ring the bell of my hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:38.08,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Yaididila leu minas sak’chwa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess will protect the sanctuary from evil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:44.18,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Dig nau e minas ligadia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The King will be the sword to cut off its hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:50.15,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Dishi di lasweina veticas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessings upon the future of the girl who’d set off again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:56.38,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Di mi woilaj molof hap’a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,even if swallowed in the vortex of a foreign world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:01:01.95,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Contas hale’ilia on shallys
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I journey ahead, holding on to my lantern
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:08.18,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Ani mita potima i ji’ulyc
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All the while thinking of the oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:14.15,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Aloviatolum stulia
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a story about a traveler
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:19.35,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Non tocias stulia
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And a story about none other than you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:26.28,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Contas hale’ilia on shallys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I journey ahead, holding on to my lantern
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:32.35,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Ani mita potima i ji’ulyc
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All the while thinking of the oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:38.42,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Zi clocs ocnoclez dinau keytyn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right, I have many guardians watching over me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:44.55,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Hap’a myukil sha lu be’iru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This fortune will surely ring the bell of my hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:13.08,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Es tuna ligali vidia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a duty to fulfill, you must live on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:18.68,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Falatost lumia diz lomo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Death may be honorable, but virtuous it is not
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:23.78,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Kuls winia nina i ji’ulyc
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your voice, raise your fist, raise your lantern
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:28.98,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Menelasm oclulu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your head and remember your bonds of trust
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:34.35,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Dililalu pipuru nodomuru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Step after step I grow more certain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:39.58,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Fal’ma invilale mam sillifri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And spurred on by the fal’ma crying out to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:44.72,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Onomabul vaniro undal’ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I run my fingers through the stream and send my words drifting off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.55,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Dina wia salame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let’s sing in place of the monument—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:55.38,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Te cant milalila ah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the song of this land that stretches out however far
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:20.62,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Hafit lasimiya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I stand still and look to the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:26.55,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Fimola shelo niconia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the faces of my beloved family
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:32.75,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Dimi woi plop’po neona
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I set off again and look to my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:38.08,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Fimola shelo lala...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the faces of my beloved friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:43.45,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Contas hale’ilia on shallys
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I journey ahead, holding on to my lantern
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:49.12,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Ani mita potima i ji’ulyc
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All the while thinking of the oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:54.62,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Zi clocs ocnoclez dinau keytyn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right, I have many guardians watching over me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:04:00.08,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Hap’a myukil sha lu be’iru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This fortune will surely ring the bell of my hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.48,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Mo lyu pe sant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, for yesterday’s wounds have already healed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.18,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Mo lata te cant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, for today like before, the land is on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:11.23,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Di mi woilaj molof hola...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, bring blessings upon the girl’s future...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:25.84,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Di mi woilaj molof hap’a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessings upon her future as she sets off again
